@inherits AdminComponentBase

<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>User Profile</strong> centralizes essential account management features such as changing your password, enabling/disabling two-factor authentication (2FA), and managing active sessions.<br />
        This section empowers users to take control of their account security and activity, ensuring a safer and more personalized experience.<br />
        All actions are secured and logged, giving transparency and peace of mind.
    </Text1>

    <Text2>
        <strong>Enhanced Security</strong>: With 2FA and session control, users can significantly reduce the risk of unauthorized access.<br />
        <strong>User Autonomy</strong>: Users can independently manage their credentials and active logins without relying on administrators.<br />
        <strong>Clear Visibility</strong>: Active sessions overview helps detect suspicious logins and take immediate action when necessary.<br />
    </Text2>

    <Text3>
        <strong>User Profile</strong> is designed to put security and control directly in users’ hands.<br />
        Whether you're updating credentials or monitoring session activity, this module simplifies personal account management.<br />
        Its straightforward interface and essential tools make it a vital part of a secure environment.
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
